		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Yurt</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Yurt_(disambiguation)" title="Yurt (disambiguation)">Yurt (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:202px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Gorskii_04412u.jpg" class="image" title="Turkmen woman at the entrance to a yurt in Turkestan; 1913 picture by Prokudin-Gorskii."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Gorskii_04412u.jpg/200px-Gorskii_04412u.jpg" width="200" height="167" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Gorskii_04412u.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
<a href="/wiki/Turkmens" title="Turkmens" class="mw-redirect">Turkmen</a> woman at the entrance to a yurt in <a href="/wiki/Turkestan" title="Turkestan">Turkestan</a>; 1913 picture by <a href="/wiki/Sergei_Mikhailovich_Prokudin-Gorskii" title="Sergei Mikhailovich Prokudin-Gorskii" class="mw-redirect">Prokudin-Gorskii</a>.</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>A <b>yurt</b> is a portable, <a href="/wiki/Felt" title="Felt">felt</a>-covered, wood <a href="/wiki/Latticework" title="Latticework">lattice</a>-framed dwelling structure used by <a href="/wiki/Nomad" title="Nomad">nomads</a> in the <a href="/wiki/Steppe" title="Steppe">steppes</a> of <a href="/wiki/Central_Asia" title="Central Asia">Central Asia</a>.</p>
